{"tid":1801610,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"咪撚再話德福搞手係鬼","createTime":"2019-12-28T18:26:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T01:42:59.000Z","uid":160376,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ce2f426aefe028be7a4af685d24da2fbf877808a","tid":1801610,"uid":160376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T18:26:38.000Z","msg":"我知大家對今次德福既事好多疑問，又收到好多資訊，但我想講搞手絕對唔係鬼<br />\n<br />\n成件事係搞手喺group send左個文宣出嚟，叫大家戴口罩保護好自己，但我地發現太少人知，所以就有人share左出去唔同既公海同channel，希望會有多啲人出<br />\n之後不停俾人forward既同時都有人加鹽加醋，叫人帶鎚仔呢啲高危野出去，係咪鬼嚟就自己諗啦。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rm5EkFE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frm5EkFE.png&h=a49acc34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n重申：最後嗰句係一直都冇<br />\n<br />\n和你shop開始前幾個鐘，有個叫<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Black grey</span>既人一入唔同既group就send咗個文宣出嚟，之後就每個人都以為係佢叫人出嚟，以為佢係搞手<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qFhWnUO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqFhWnUO.jpg&h=473b9a77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後喺6點幾7點嗰陣，呢位Black grey又唔小心喺group send咗張記者既相出嚟，但係嗰個角度影到記者既位置只係得兩個green object企喺到，而曾經其中一個green object都有拎過部電話對住記者，所以black grey已fc係鬼<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/防暴警疑拍記者照片-上載-tg-公海群組-沒回應是否-send-錯-group/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E7%96%91%E6%8B%8D%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87-%E4%B8%8A%E8%BC%89-tg-%E5%85%AC%E6%B5%B7%E7%BE%A4%E7%B5%84-%E6%B2%92%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6-send-%E9%8C%AF-group%2F&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNfrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=58c329f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E7%96%91%E6%8B%8D%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87-%E4%B8%8A%E8%BC%89-tg-%E5%85%AC%E6%B5%B7%E7%BE%A4%E7%B5%84-%E6%B2%92%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6-send-%E9%8C%AF-group%2F&h=79b93a79\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/防暴警疑拍記者照片-上載-tg-公海群組-沒回應是否-send-錯-group/</a><br />\n<br />\n但就係因為Black grey曾經喺group send過個文宣post出嚟，大家就誤以為佢係搞手，加埋send錯group呢件事，就令大家以為今次既活動搞手係鬼<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以我重申：搞手唔撚係鬼！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n經歷咗咁多個月，大家係咪已經忘記咗咩係Fact check?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家下次再捉鬼前不妨fact check下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我希望大家唔好再傳搞手係鬼既message，唔好再話佢係鬼，佢自己出嚟澄清過，大家都幫佢澄清過，仲係唔信既都冇辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">但當然衷心希望大家可以還搞手一個清白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"3efaacb2821ddb40ef9f35d317ab64bef1a2d82b","tid":1801610,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T18:29:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃色經濟圈的障礙<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801188\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1801188</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2e8c00c6b828312f738345226ecd81ff12bebd15","tid":1801610,"uid":160376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T18:48:27.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27c8f0a8b61966cf464a9b5dcc82a7e596e5b686","tid":1801610,"uid":181339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T01:29:15.000Z","msg":"推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a13dd60027262cb040d6c181fa2a0f3f811ec41","tid":1801610,"uid":187262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T01:35:23.000Z","msg":"已經唔重要啦 1月1見啦"},{"pid":"8f9117219a66d284bee768f8d7fa6e75e512f8b5","tid":1801610,"uid":304856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce2f426aefe028be7a4af685d24da2fbf877808a","tid":18